author: Digital Foundry
description:
Digital Foundry is now fully independent! Join the DF Supporter Program and support the team: https://bit.ly/3jEGjvx

Strix Halo - in the form of the top-end Ryzen AI Max+ 395 is the most powerful PC APU AMD has ever made, capable of providing remarkable performance in the smallest of form-factors. Rich takes a look at the GMKTec Evo-X2, which allows us to run the full gamut of Strix Halo performance testing - up against desktop CPUs and GPUs, and - inevitably - Sony's PlayStation 5.
